Exactly what i wanted! Do you have any idea how hard it is to find Connan the Barbarian and Connan the Destroyer with AC-3/5.1 audio? Thank goodness this came as advertised.

The item I received has two discs with Connan the Barbarian and Connan the Destroyer on one and The Scorpion King and Kull the Conqueror on the other.  All moves came with AC-3/5.1 audio tracks and English subtitles.
The two Conan movies are classic. Great action films. The Scorpion King is a lot of fun to. Kull is alright, I do like Kevin Sorbo though.
just what I was looking for.

Got this mainly for the Conan films.  I grew up with them and they will always be timeless classics to me.

No special features.  Just bare bones widescreen 5.1 basic dvd versions of all 4 films.  Still a great deal at just $5.
So many good movies in one box!!!
I love these movies so this was a great buy for me. Conan is my favorite Barbarian film series.

I am very pleased with this CD collection. I like to watch action and adventure movies and I believe that I now have some first rate movies. I always like Arnold Schwarzenegger action/drama movies, and the Conan series is one of my favorite. This collection also has Kevin Sorbo ( star of Hercules)--so I will be entertained for a good long time. Shipping was very fast--I am Amazon Prime member (2-day on time delivery). Got no complaints on this purchase, I strongly recommend seller and I plan to make more purchases very soon.

I saw and picked up this same pack at a large local store and is indeed quite a deal. As for how the movies are offered, you get two discs, one with the two Conan movies. And the others on a second disc. You select between the two films when loading a disc and it plays...and that's it.

Not the best deal ever due to the lack of anything beyond the movies, but for a buck a movie that is good enough. For reference, other discount 4-packs like the TCM Classics Sci-fi have many extras per movies with full dedicated menus and are highly recommended.
